               <p>SECOND COUNT. For falsely uttering and publishing, as true, a certain forged deed, with the like intent, knowing it to be forged.</p>
               <p>THIRD AND FOURTH COUNTS. stating it to be to defraud 
               <persName id="t18170416-74-victim569" type="victimName">
                  Milward 
                  Oliver
               <interp inst="t18170416-74-victim569" type="surname" value="Oliver"></interp>
